3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with the recognition of emotions, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image processing and analysis, which is a subfield of multimedia. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper deals with recognizing emotions from facial expressions, which has applications in human-computer interaction.
